{"tid":2083122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周浩鼎稱如制裁商業機構及人士　最終只會傷害美國利益","createTime":"2020-06-28T14:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T14:34:59.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b236f3c59eb54933b766d24a4916942e25db0f","tid":2083122,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"周浩鼎稱如制裁商業機構及人士　最終只會傷害美國利益<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534303-20200626.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534303-20200626.htm&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8Z1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=0948c939\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534303-20200626.htm&h=3c754360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534303-20200626.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國參議院一致通過《香港自治法案》，可制裁美方認為損害香港自治的人士及企業。民建聯周浩鼎批評美國政客，干預香港事務及中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎表示，美國上次通過《香港人權與民主法案》時，他已清楚表明香港事務和中國內政不容外國勢力干涉，批評美方不但沒停手，更進一步干預。<br />\n<br />\n對於美方打算制裁支持港區國安法的商業機構和人士，周浩鼎說，國際與香港之間有很多營商合作，有關做法最終只會傷害美國利益。"},{"pid":"4a09d83038b1218a29d1259c2bde8b778e823fa3","tid":2083122,"uid":166729,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"損美國1000, 損支那100000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078507df8c6616d6c2cc1fe017f9b0c9f69143be","tid":2083122,"uid":290883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:07:00.000Z","msg":"人哋唔撚 care，人哋大撚把本錢呀，傻閪！"},{"pid":"efc6187bd1192799688f05d3045527eea9aac88f","tid":2083122,"uid":245310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:07:24.000Z","msg":"講黎講去都係三篤屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2c3e3897deb825dd3f0dbd4cc037313b3cc40e","tid":2083122,"uid":231480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"人哋對